Audio

Class Track

  • java.lang.Object
    • Audio.Track

  • public class Track
extends java.lang.Object
    Track/channel class represents a given line of data within a mixer. A line then needs to be filled with some audio data which may be from recorded input or .wav samples. Track may be a superclass of other tracks that can be created. We may have audio data (recorded and sample based) as well as MIDI data for a track.
